nd Fees\n**SpaceX Bridge Loan**\n*   **Variable Rate:** Term SOFR + 0.75% to 1.75% margin, OR Base Rate (highest of Fed Funds + 0.5%, Prime, Term SOFR + 1.00%, or 1.00%) + 0.00% to 0.75% margin (depending on debt rating).\n*   **Duration Fees:** 0.125% of outstanding principal on the 1st anniversary; 0.25% on the 15-month anniversary.\n*   **Effective Rate:** 4.58% as of March 31, 2026.\n\n**SpaceX Credit Facility**\n*   **Variable Rate:** Term SOFR + 0.75% to 1.25% margin, OR Base Rate + 0.00% to 0.25% margin.\n*   **Alternative Currencies:** SONIA (GBP) or EURIBOR (EUR) + applicable margin.\n*   **Commitment Fee:** 0.07% (amended to 0.06%) to 0.11% per annum on the unused portion.\n\n**X Senior Unsecured Notes**\n*   **X 2027 Notes:** Fixed at 3.875% (payable semi-annually).\n*   **X 2030 Notes:** Fixed at 5.000% (payable semi-annually).\n\n**xAI Revolving Line of Credit**\n*   **Variable Rate:** 30-day average SOFR + ISDA spread adjustment + 40 basis points.\n\n**Other Financings**\n*   **Equipment/Infrastructure Debt:** Average fixed interest rate of 4.4% (as of Mar 31, 2026) and 5.5% (as of Dec 31, 2025).\n\n*(Note: Extinguished X B-1, X B-3, xAI Fixed/Floating loans, and Bridge facilities carried rates ranging from Adjusted SOFR + 4.50% up to fixed rates of 12.50%, with effective yields up to 12.48% prior to their repayment).*\n\n---\n\n### 3. Maturity Schedule & Repayment Terms\n**Future Scheduled Principal Maturities (As of March 31, 2026)**\n| Year | Principal Amount |\n| :--- | :--- |\n| **2026** (remaining 9 months) | $801 million |\n| **2027** | $21,540 million |\n| **2028** | $1,938 million |\n| **2029** | $2,393 million |\n| **2030** | $2,460 million |\n| **Thereafter** | $— |\n| **Total** | **$29,132 million** |\n\n**Key Maturity & Extension Details:**\n*   **SpaceX Bridge Loan:** Matures September 2, 2027. Includes two optional 3-month extensions (subject to a 0.25% extension fee per period), pushing the final maturity to March 2028. Prepayable at an